WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.710
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:05.749
Lord. Easter weekend, my favorite time

00:00:05.759 --> 00:00:08.070
of the year. Well, praise the Lord, I'm

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:09.910
excited. It's time to be grateful. It's

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:12.790
time to be thankful for all that Jesus

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:15.910
has done for every single one of us.

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:18.550
It's a time to reflect. I

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:21.189
always just sit and watch my kids

00:00:21.199 --> 00:00:23.990
and the church things that we go to,

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.470
and it makes me

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:28.790
go inward and think

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:32.870
about all that Jesus did—all his

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:36.069
suffering, all that he did to break the

00:00:36.079 --> 00:00:39.030
chains of bondage off of our lives so that

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:42.869
we could walk free. You know, I

00:00:42.879 --> 00:00:44.950
bring out this video. I've brought out

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:47.350
a lot of videos the last couple of

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:48.950
days that I've already brought out

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:51.510
before, and I usually do it once a year. These

00:00:51.510 --> 00:00:51.520
are

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:54.630
the experiences that I've had with

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:57.750
the Lord that have changed me, and

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:00.069
they're too good just to let get buried

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:02.069
in the algorithm. They get weighed down at

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:03.750
the bottom of the feed and people forget

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:06.149
about them. So Braden, Diana, and

00:01:06.149 --> 00:01:06.159
I

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:08.950
bring those videos out again

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.750
because we believe there's life still in

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:14.630
those videos, in that experience that I

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:16.950
had with the Lord—that word that

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:19.910
the Lord gave to tell you all about his

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.910
coming and where the tribulation

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:23.710
was. And now this

00:01:23.720 --> 00:01:26.950
one is about his crucifixion. I was

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:28.870
sitting on the side of my bed one night

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:30.630
and I was asking the Lord because one of

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:32.469
the people of the church called and

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:34.950
said, "Brandon, I've been suffering

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:37.670
with arthritis for years. My hands are

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:40.149
crippled up. I can't move my hands. I've

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:43.030
been in so much pain. How come you think

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:44.710
I've been a preacher?"He told me all

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:46.069
the things that he had done

00:01:46.079 --> 00:01:47.870
and how he's still

00:01:47.880 --> 00:01:50.230
suffering. And so I thought,

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:52.789
"I don't know. I'm overcoming stuff

00:01:52.799 --> 00:01:55.270
myself. My daughter's overcoming, and

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:57.109
I've been standing in

00:01:57.109 --> 00:01:57.119
faith."And

00:01:57.119 --> 00:01:58.709
I told him all my sob story, you

00:01:58.719 --> 00:01:59.990
know, after you

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.590
tell your sob stories of

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:03.830
everything you go through and

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:05.510
you listen to each other, but it still

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:07.510
didn't fix the problem because you still

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:09.830
are overcoming what you're overcoming.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:11.830
So I sat on the side of

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:14.150
the bed and I said, "Lord, would you

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:16.390
please explain to me why all the body of

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:19.350
Christ is not healed? Why are we not

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.510
experiencing the glory? Why

00:02:21.520 --> 00:02:24.070
have we not seen the

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:26.110
manifestation of what we're believing

00:02:26.110 --> 00:02:26.120
for?"So

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:29.470
I just went to

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:33.589
sleep and all of a sudden, in that

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:37.350
sleeping time, I had a dream. Now you

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:40.229
know when you have a dream that is just

00:02:40.229 --> 00:02:40.239
an

00:02:40.239 --> 00:02:43.270
over-the-top dream,

00:02:43.270 --> 00:02:43.280
where

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:45.350
you can smell things? This was like I

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:47.910
was out of my body in my dream. This was

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:51.990
such a supernatural dream that it

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:53.990
was real. All of a sudden, I was

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.470
standing in this courtyard. It was

00:02:56.480 --> 00:02:59.030
hot outside, probably about 80

00:02:59.030 --> 00:02:59.040
degrees.

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:00.390
I could actually feel the

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:02.149
temperature. I could feel the sun

00:03:02.159 --> 00:03:03.589
hitting me. You know, whenever you're

00:03:03.599 --> 00:03:05.430
standing out there and there's no breeze?

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:07.750
In the dream, I could feel how hot it

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:10.550
was. And I looked around me and all of a

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:12.710
sudden to my right hand, Jesus was

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:15.430
standing there. And then I realized

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:18.550
where I was. I was taken back in time

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:21.509
and I was at the crucifixion because I

00:03:21.519 --> 00:03:24.229
could see Jesus. The

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:28.070
Jesus that I was seeing had oily skin.

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:32.229
He had his shirt off. His

00:03:32.239 --> 00:03:34.309
skin was dirty looking. He looked like

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:37.910
he had dirt on him and he was being led

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:39.630
to the whipping

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:43.110
post. They took his hands, ladies

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:45.470
and gentlemen, and they put them in

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:48.390
shackles and they tied him to a whipping

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:51.030
post in front of my face. And I could

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:54.190
see the

00:03:54.190 --> 00:03:54.200
stanchion

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:57.750
right here with this

00:03:57.750 --> 00:03:57.760
metal-looking

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:00.789
hoop. And they put his

00:04:00.799 --> 00:04:03.670
hands and latched his hands on that

00:04:03.670 --> 00:04:03.680
hoop-looking

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:05.910
thing. They put his hands

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:08.470
up there like that. And there was a man

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:11.429
that was dressed in solid black over on

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:14.630
his right hand. He was probably

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:19.430
about 300 pounds. He was a

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:22.069
big guy, bigger than me. This man was

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:25.030
big, and his body structure was big.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.870
His shoulders were big, but he was

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:29.670
bald-headed with a shaved head.

00:04:32.479 --> 00:04:34.790
And on his

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:36.430
left

00:04:36.440 --> 00:04:40.550
side was a man in Roman garb.

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:43.510
He had a Roman helmet on,

00:04:43.510 --> 00:04:43.520
a

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:46.070
Roman outfit on—the

00:04:46.070 --> 00:04:46.080
leather-looking outfit.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:50.310
It was all just

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:53.510
like you see in Roman times.

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:56.710
Both men had

00:04:56.720 --> 00:05:00.390
the cat-o'-nine-tails in their hands. And I

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:04.790
saw the one man take... well, first I saw

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:07.430
them pull his beard. I saw them rip out

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:09.590
his beard. They were

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.629
punching Jesus in the face. I could see

00:05:12.639 --> 00:05:15.350
Jesus's head bounce around as they were

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.950
just beating him in the face and

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:18.710
punching him. They were ripping his

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.790
beard out of his face. They were pushing

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:23.110
on the crown of thorns on his head

00:05:23.110 --> 00:05:23.120
because

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:25.189
he had a crown of thorns on his head as

00:05:25.199 --> 00:05:27.749
he was there.

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:30.390
His skin looked like it had been welped

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:33.350
up. He looked like he had been beaten,

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:36.070
and his back already

00:05:36.080 --> 00:05:38.469
looked bruised from somebody beating on

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:41.749
him. His body already looked like

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:43.670
it was—you know, whenever you see

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:46.950
skin that was already like you were

00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.670
beaten with sticks? He looked like he

00:05:49.670 --> 00:05:49.680
had

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:52.629
purple

00:05:52.629 --> 00:05:52.639
burst

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:54.790
blood vessels that were already popped

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:57.510
all over his back. He looked like

00:05:57.510 --> 00:05:57.520
someone

00:05:57.520 --> 00:05:59.830
who had been in a bad

00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:02.950
fight and had lost, totally

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:05.749
purple from his body being beaten

00:06:05.759 --> 00:06:08.790
through his olive skin. And you

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:11.270
could see the glistening on his back

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:14.469
that looked like oil from the sweat from

00:06:14.479 --> 00:06:16.469
how hot it was outside. It was about

00:06:16.479 --> 00:06:18.870
80 or 85 degrees, but

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:20.550
you could see the

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:23.990
oils from his skin. And I just remember

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:27.189
looking at his body and I saw him being

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:29.990
lifted up like this, above his

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:32.790
head. And I saw his

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:36.070
bruises all over his body and

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:38.550
his face, and he had blood from where

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:41.270
the beard was being ripped out of his

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:43.670
face. There was blood dripping and

00:06:43.670 --> 00:06:43.680
it

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.670
looked

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:46.950
like what you would look like if

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:49.670
you had hair ripped out of your head.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:51.830
And I could see the thorns, like I said.

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:54.710
So these men were taking the thorns and

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:56.870
they were pushing them on his head more

00:06:56.880 --> 00:06:59.350
because they had things on their hands,

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.029
so it wasn't hurting them, but it was

00:07:01.039 --> 00:07:03.670
hurting Jesus. And I could see he was in

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:09.830
tremendous pain.

00:07:09.840 --> 00:07:13.189
As I stood there with Jesus on this side

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:16.390
in his glorified body, I could see him

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:18.150
and he was watching on, and we were

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:23.950
looking at him being

00:07:23.960 --> 00:07:27.350
whipped. And I saw the one man in the

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:31.029
black outfit take that

00:07:31.029 --> 00:07:31.039
cat-o'-nine-tails

00:07:31.039 --> 00:07:34.469
and he went and he whipped him. And

00:07:34.479 --> 00:07:37.589
whenever he did, I saw flesh stripped off

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:40.309
of his body like it was just

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:42.309
big chunks. It was not just like a

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:44.070
little bitty scratch. Ladies and

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:49.950
gentlemen, what I saw before me was

00:07:49.960 --> 00:07:53.029
horrific. And all that came off of his

00:07:53.039 --> 00:07:55.350
body and it just scratched him deep to

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:56.350
the

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:59.110
bones. Then they took the other man and

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:01.350
he took that other side and they whipped

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:03.830
him again on this side. And as one was

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.589
whipping this side, the other... and

00:08:05.599 --> 00:08:07.270
they would take turns, and each one

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:10.029
would whip. It wasn't a

00:08:10.039 --> 00:08:13.189
break. One would whip, then the other, to

00:08:13.199 --> 00:08:16.230
the point where his flesh was dripping

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:19.350
off of his body. Every time

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:22.070
he was being hit, it

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:23.830
was like he was being moved and he was

00:08:23.840 --> 00:08:25.990
screaming

00:08:25.990 --> 00:08:26.000
in

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:29.350
agony.

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:33.750
All I

00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:37.149
could do while I was standing there

00:08:37.149 --> 00:08:37.159
was say,

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:40.149
"Stop! You've got to stop!"but nobody could

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:42.790
hear me. I said, "Oh, God, they've got

00:08:42.800 --> 00:08:45.430
to stop!"because I could see his body

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:47.990
in the pain that he was

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:51.030
feeling. Because his arms were above his

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:53.590
head, it was going around his chest

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:56.389
and it was taking his skin off of his

00:08:56.399 --> 00:08:59.430
body in chunks—not just a little

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:03.190
bit, but deep, deep wounds were just

00:09:03.200 --> 00:09:05.430
being lashed and scraped and ripped out

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:09.269
of his body as he was taking all of the

00:09:09.279 --> 00:09:13.590
stripes for us.

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:15.190
Blood was dripping down him and he was

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:18.550
just in a pool of blood all around him.

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:23.070
And Jesus said this to me: "What

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:27.269
part of 'By my stripes you are

00:09:27.269 --> 00:09:27.279
healed'do

00:09:27.279 --> 00:09:30.829
you not understand?"He

00:09:30.829 --> 00:09:30.839
was

00:09:30.839 --> 00:09:32.990
pointing at

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:35.269
himself. He said, "I took all that on

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:38.470
the cross for you. I took all sickness,

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:41.269
all disease, everything for you. And I

00:09:41.279 --> 00:09:45.990
said in my word, 'By my stripes you

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.550
are

00:09:47.550 --> 00:09:47.560
healed.'"He

00:09:47.560 --> 00:09:49.990
said, "Brandon, I want to tell

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:54.829
you something.

00:09:54.839 --> 00:09:57.150
The same

00:09:57.160 --> 00:10:01.829
way you believe that you're saved is the

00:10:01.839 --> 00:10:05.990
same way you believe for your

00:10:05.990 --> 00:10:06.000
healing."He

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:08.630
said, "Brandon, if anybody was to

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.870
tell you that you were not saved, you

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:12.870
would fight them, wouldn't you? You

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:14.630
would say, 'Oh, I know I'm saved. You

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:16.630
know it,'because you're that convinced

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:19.910
in your heart. But yet, you

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:22.949
have nothing to assure you other than

00:10:22.959 --> 00:10:25.150
your faith that you

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:28.949
are. You have no way of believing other

00:10:28.959 --> 00:10:31.269
than by what you've heard me say,

00:10:31.269 --> 00:10:31.279
or

00:10:31.279 --> 00:10:34.150
the preacher say, that you are saved by

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:36.630
grace through faith. And you believed

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:38.310
and you received it and you just latched

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:41.350
on to it, but you're convinced, no matter

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:43.990
if you sin or whatever, that you believe

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:45.230
that you're

00:10:45.230 --> 00:10:45.240
saved."I

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:48.389
said, "That's right."And he

00:10:48.399 --> 00:10:50.069
said, "And if they would tell you you

00:10:50.079 --> 00:10:52.389
weren't saved, you would fight them. You

00:10:52.399 --> 00:10:54.710
would argue with them and say, 'No, I

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:56.710
know I'm saved.'They say, 'No, I don't

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:57.990
believe you're saved.''No, I know I'm

00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:59.430
saved. You're not going to tell me I'm

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:00.790
not saved.'"I said, "That's exactly

00:11:00.790 --> 00:11:00.800
right,"because

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:03.190
I could see myself

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:06.230
in this experience saying

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:09.190
that as somebody was telling me, "I don't

00:11:09.200 --> 00:11:10.389
believe you're saved."I said, "Well, I

00:11:10.399 --> 00:11:13.030
know I'm saved. I know I'm saved."And I

00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:14.710
was fully persuaded that I know I'm

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:16.230
saved. But yet, I had no outward

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.990
appearance, because I know when I fall

00:11:18.000 --> 00:11:20.710
and I mess up every day, somebody does.

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:22.710
But yet, I'm still convinced that Jesus

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:24.470
Christ forgave me of my sins and my name

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:26.310
is written in the Lamb's Book of

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:27.750
Life.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:33.870
He said, "Healing and salvation are the

00:11:33.880 --> 00:11:38.550
same. By my stripes, you are healed. I

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:40.630
took it on the cross for you, just like

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:43.430
I took your sin on the cross. I took

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:45.269
your poverty. I became poor that you

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:48.470
might be rich. I took it all for you,

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:50.750
just like I did

00:11:50.760 --> 00:11:53.870
salvation. But yet you believe in the

00:11:53.880 --> 00:11:56.069
salvation more than what you believe in

00:11:56.079 --> 00:11:59.350
the healing. When you believe the same

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:02.509
way you believe for your

00:12:02.519 --> 00:12:04.870
salvation, then nobody can talk you out

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:06.350
of

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:08.550
it. It's the same way you believe for

00:12:08.560 --> 00:12:10.069
your healing."He said, "When you believe

00:12:10.079 --> 00:12:12.310
it the same way, Brandon,

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:14.509
that's where your manifestation

00:12:14.519 --> 00:12:18.629
comes. Believing it whenever you don't

00:12:18.639 --> 00:12:21.030
see it,

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:24.110
believing it when you still feel the

00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:26.910
symptom of what you're going

00:12:26.910 --> 00:12:26.920
through."He

00:12:26.920 --> 00:12:30.430
said, "When you believe

